&nbsp;spiritual people themselves hav=\r\ne&nbsp;clearly done so on different occassions. Vivekananda says Ramakrishn=\r\na&nbsp;a greater spiritual man. I take his words as true. Period.&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DI=\r\nV&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV&gt;Dear All,&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV&gt;This is hardly a=\r\n matter of&nbsp;parochialism. Please do not unnecessarily complicate&nbsp;a=\r\n simple discussion. I think&nbsp;the discussion has been misunderstood. Eit=\r\nher&nbsp;go ontu Twitter and read the whole discussion point by point, or s=\r\nimple ignore it and keep doing your own stuff.&nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/DIV=\r\n&gt;\n&lt;DIV&gt;-Regards&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV&gt;&nbsp;Rajarshi&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;BR&gt;=\r\n&nbsp;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;EM&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;\n&lt;DIV class=3DMsoNormal&gt;&lt;STRONG&gt;&lt;SPAN style=\r\n=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY: Verdana; COLOR: navy; FONT-SIZE: 10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#0000=\r\n00 face=3D&quot;Times New Roman&quot;&gt;\n&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;SPAN style=3D&quot;COLOR: #000066&quot; class=\r\n=3DApple-style-span&gt;&lt;SPAN style=3D&quot;FONT-SIZE: medium&quot; class=3DApple-style-s=\r\npan&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#a2a2a2 size=3D3&gt;Bazeecha-e-atfal hain duniya mere aage.&lt;=\r\n/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;SPAN style=3D&quot;COLOR: #000066&quot; class=\r\n=3DApple-style-span&gt;&lt;SPAN style=3D&quot;FONT-SIZE: medium&quot; class=3DApple-style-s=\r\npan&gt;&lt;FONT size=3D3&gt;&lt;FONT color=3D#a2a2a2&gt;Hota hain shab-o-roz tamasha mere =\r\naage&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/FONT&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/B&gt;&lt;/DIV&gt;\n&lt;DIV&gt;&lt;B&gt;&lt;SPAN style=3D&quot;COLOR: #0=\r\n00066&quot; class=3DApple-style-span&gt;&lt;SPAN style=3D&quot;FONT-SIZE: medium&quot; class=3DA=\r\npple-style-span&gt;&lt;SPAN style=3D&quot;COLOR: #000099&quot; class=3DApple-style-span&gt;&lt;SP=\r\nAN style=3D